
Overview of adv firmly

The adv firmly has 3 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (11) firm, firmly, steadfastly, unwaveringly -- (with resolute determination; "we firmly believed it"; "you must stand firm")
2. (5) securely, firmly -- (in a secure manner; in a manner free from danger; "she held the child securely")
3. (2) hard, firmly -- (with firmness; "held hard to the railing")
